<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL11">
<l>oruvillā lōṅku munnī raṉaittula kaṅka ḷuyyac</l>
<l>ceruvilē yarakkar kōṉaic ceṟṟanañ cēva kaṉār</l>
<l>maruviya periya kōyil matiṭṭiru varaṅka meṉṉā</l>
<l>karuvilē tiruvi lātīr kālattaik kaḻikkiṉ ṟīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O you  people who—not [having received] good fortune [while being] in the womb—</l>
<l>do not say</l>
<l rend="indent">‘The walled Śrīraṅgam is the great temple</l>
<l rend="indent">joined by our Warrior who vanquished in battle the king of Rakshasas</l>
<l rend="indent">having blocked the rising sea by means of a unique bow,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the worlds are saved!’!</l>
<l>You are wasting [your] time!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
